snippet.title: Undead Inc. - Official Announcement Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the announcement trailer for Undead Inc., an upcoming high-risk, high-reward resource management simulator where you establish and manage a local subsidiary of the Endswell Medical Corporation. In Undead Inc., build, manage staff, conduct research, and trade in both cutting-edge medical treatments and bleeding-edge bioweapons. Undead Inc. is coming to PC.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerofGaming
